<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得查出布洛姆市长发生了什么事！”罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看着朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，朋友们。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我忘记带午饭钱了。我们学校见吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能借给你。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，罗西已经不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西很快到了市政府。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，那栋大楼已经不见了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真是奇怪。”罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我最好先找到史密斯侦探！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他也许知道美罗城发生了什么事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞到警察总局。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好！”罗西喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那栋楼也不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”一个微弱的声音喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯？”罗西看了看四周，什么也没看到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奇怪。”她想，“我是听到有人叫我的名字。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个声音又叫了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！我在下面！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西往下看去。“噢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探站在地上，旁边有一棵蒲公英。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看起来只有一厘米高。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看上去很不高兴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看起来您有一个‘小’问题，史密斯侦探。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探皱起眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不好玩儿，火箭女孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能告诉我发生什么事了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们听到了一个奇怪的声音。”侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后，警察总局开始变小。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里面的人也开始变小。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我从窗户里跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，一个巨人把大楼捡起来带走了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158933</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西挠挠头。“美罗城的新大楼也变小了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，没有道理啊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为什么会有人把大楼变小了呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道。”侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173700</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我们需要查清楚，我不能一直这样子......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，传来一阵巨响。嗡！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西转过身去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一栋大楼正在缩小！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好了！”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她低下头看着史密斯侦探。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您在这儿等着，侦探先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我去看看怎么回事儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞到美罗城上空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她又听到那个声音。嗡！嗡！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又有两栋大楼变小后不见了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西落地以后看看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用超级听力去听。“嘻嘻！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听起来好像是一个小女孩儿在咯咯地笑。”罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“声音是从停车场的另一边儿传来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞到停车场上方向地面望去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个穿着宇航服的小女孩儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手里拿着一个奇怪的仪器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把仪器瞄准了熊雕像。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗡！熊雕像变小了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小女孩儿把它放进了口袋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”罗西喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是那个小女孩儿把东西变小带走的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>